    • Field Detail

      • NATIVE_DIR

        public static final java.lang.String NATIVE_DIR
        constants for directory names where native and java libs are stored in a toolbox. For a toolbox to know where these things are and have them loaded, and exposed, these naming convention must be followed.

        The OS-specific dir names should all be within a 'nativ' dir.
